    <h5>Welcome to www.rollformedshapes.com </h5>
    <p align="left">SRFC specializes in custom roll formed metal shapes. It is our mission to provide each customer with structurally sound parts at affordable prices.&nbsp;</p>
    <p align="left">Experience shows that roll forming offers more options and benefits than many other processes. The ability to incorporate several secondary operations into the roll forming line significantly reduces overall cost for our customers.&nbsp; </p>
    <p align="left" class="standout">Roll Forming is a process in which a strip of metal, usually in coil form, is continuously passed through a series of roller dies and progressively formed to the desired shape. </p>
    <p align="left">In many cases roll forming eliminates multiple stage production, sub-assembly and finishing operations. Any number of subassembly operation can be continuously combined in the roll forming operation.<br>
To learn more about roll forming and its benefits read <a href="faq.htm" title="FAQ's">frequently asked questions about roll forming</a> or feel free to <a href="faq.htm#Ask a question..." title="Ask a question">ask a question</a>.</p>
    <p align="left"><a href="quoteform.htm" title="Easy fill-in Quote Form" class="emphasis">Get a quote</a><br>
                          <br>
                          To obtain pricing for a custom part fill out the online <a href="quoteform.htm" title="Quote Form">Quote Request Form</a> or contact our <a href="javascript:location='mailto:\u0073\u0061\u006c\u0065\u0073\u0040\u0072\u006f\u006c\u006c\u0066\u006f\u0072\u006d\u0065\u0064\u0073\u0068\u0061\u0070\u0065\u0073\u002e\u0063\u006f\u006d';void 0">Sales Team</a>
.&nbsp;</p>
    <p align="left" class="emphasis"><a title="Easy fill-in Quote Form" href="equipment.htm">Machinery Sales</a></p>
    <p align="left">SRFC now offers roll forming equipment including rolling mills and presses as well as lathes and hydraulic equipment.<br>
      <a href="equipment.htm">Click here</a> for a complete list of roll forming machinery available today. To learn more <a href="javascript:location='mailto:\u0063\u006f\u006e\u0073\u0075\u006c\u0074\u0069\u006e\u0067\u0040\u0072\u006f\u006c\u006c\u0066\u006f\u0072\u006d\u0065\u0064\u0073\u0068\u0061\u0070\u0065\u0073\u002e\u0063\u006f\u006d';void 0">contact us</a>
 to today to speak with a member of our team. </p>
    <p align="left" class="emphasis"><br>
      <a href="consulting.htm" title="Roll Forming Consulting">Roll Forming Consulting &amp; Training Team</a>&nbsp;</p>
    <p align="left"> Do you have an existing roll forming line that needs improvement?&nbsp;<br>
      Increase productivity, learn to hold tolerances and extend tool and equipment life.</p>
    <p align="left" class="emphasis"><br>
    <a href="yourplant.htm">Your Plant</a></p>
    <p align="left">Is your company planning a shutdown for phasing or maintenance? <br>
